    <div class="container">
      <aside class="left-col">
        <h1>Water</h1>
        <p>Water is a basic necessity for life. However, having too much or too little water can be problematic. Clean Foundation can help you with water conservation inside your home and with rainwater management on your property.<br />
 <br />
Quality is just as important as quantity when it comes to water, so Clean also provides opportunities for you to take action to improve the health of your watershed and manage the waste water you produce. Our work includes stream restoration projects to improve habitat quality for fish, an innovative Atlantic Reef Ball program that fosters healthier marine environments,  and the award-winning Ship-to-Shore waste reduction program.</p>
        <a href="http://clean.ns.ca/programs/water/" class="btn">Learn more</a>
      </aside>
