    <div class="container">
      <aside class="left-col">
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
<blockquote><p>Clean Foundation provides the knowledge, tools and inspiration needed to encourage the individual actions that add up to positive environmental change. We work for a clean climate and clean water – and to help reach these green goals, we foster and support clean leaders.</p></blockquote>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>

